    "Fontanesi et al. [229] investigated joint predictive beamforming and trajectory design for the aerial ISAC systems where a UAV acted as an aerial ISAC-BS to communicate with the ground users and sense the target.",
    "They proposed a dual DNN to learn the mappings from the position of the UAV to the optimal beamforming vector and user association directly.",
    "Resource allocationISAC can integrate the communication and sensing into a unified platform and allow them to share the multi-domain resource, such as time, frequency, and spatial domain.",
    "Due to the shared resource, efficient resource allocation is critical to satisfy the needs of communication and sensing.",
    "However, the resource allocation of ISAC usually involves complicated non-convex optimization problems with highdimensional optimization variables, which makes the traditional algorithms intractable."
